{"thig11.1:0.1":"Therigatha 11.1 ","thig11.1:0.2":"Dvadasakanipata ","thig11.1:0.3":"Uppalavannatherigatha ","thig11.1:1.1":"“Ubho mata ca dhita ca, ","thig11.1:1.2":"mayam asum sapattiyo; ","thig11.1:1.3":"Tassa me ahu samvego, ","thig11.1:1.4":"abbhuto lomahamsano. ","thig11.1:2.1":"Dhiratthu kama asuci, ","thig11.1:2.2":"duggandha bahukantaka; ","thig11.1:2.3":"Yattha mata ca dhita ca, ","thig11.1:2.4":"sabhariya mayam ahum. ","thig11.1:3.1":"Kamesvadinavam disva, ","thig11.1:3.2":"nekkhammam datthu khemato; ","thig11.1:3.3":"Sa pabbajjim rajagahe, ","thig11.1:3.4":"agarasmanagariyam. ","thig11.1:4.1":"Pubbenivasam janami, ","thig11.1:4.2":"dibbacakkhu visodhitam; ","thig11.1:4.3":"Cetopariccanananca, ","thig11.1:4.4":"sotadhatu visodhita. ","thig11.1:5.1":"Iddhipi me sacchikata, ","thig11.1:5.2":"patto me asavakkhayo; ","thig11.1:5.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","thig11.1:5.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","thig11.1:6.1":"Iddhiya abhinimmitva, ","thig11.1:6.2":"caturassam ratham aham; ","thig11.1:6.3":"Buddhassa pade vanditva, ","thig11.1:6.4":"lokanathassa tadino”. ","thig11.1:7.1":"“Supupphitaggam upagamma padapam, ","thig11.1:7.2":"Eka tuvam titthasi salamule; ","thig11.1:7.3":"Na capi te dutiyo atthi koci, ","thig11.1:7.4":"Bale na tvam bhayasi dhuttakanam”. ","thig11.1:8.1":"“Satam sahassanipi dhuttakanam, ","thig11.1:8.2":"Samagata edisaka bhaveyyum; ","thig11.1:8.3":"Lomam na inje napi sampavedhe, ","thig11.1:8.4":"Kim me tuvam mara karissaseko. ","thig11.1:9.1":"Esa antaradhayami, ","thig11.1:9.2":"kucchim va pavisami te; ","thig11.1:9.3":"Bhamukantare titthami, ","thig11.1:9.4":"titthantim mam na dakkhasi. ","thig11.1:10.1":"Cittamhi vasibhutaham, ","thig11.1:10.2":"iddhipada subhavita; ","thig11.1:10.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","thig11.1:10.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","thig11.1:11.1":"Sattisulupama kama, ","thig11.1:11.2":"khandhasam adhikuttana; ","thig11.1:11.3":"Yam tvam ‘kamaratim’ brusi, ","thig11.1:11.4":"‘arati’ dani sa mama. ","thig11.1:12.1":"Sabbattha vihata nandi, ","thig11.1:12.2":"Tamokhandho padalito; ","thig11.1:12.3":"Evam janahi papima, ","thig11.1:12.4":"Nihato tvamasi antaka”ti. ","thig11.1:13.1":"… Uppalavanna theri …. ","thig11.1:14.1":"Dvadasakanipato nitthito. "}